Hi there!

What's new in our latest update:

— added new "Wordsman" game: have fun making dozens of shorter words out of a longer one;
— updated the UI design and ehnanced the Vocabulary Builder settings;
— fixed various bugs to enhance stability of the app.

Stay tuned.

Hello to English lovers!

We have updated the design of video puzzles, grammar lessons, and personal vocabulary. Information is now more structured, and the pages look better.
Also, you can add whole phrases to personal vocabulary and work with them.

Bugs are fixed too :)
